    "sections": {
      "PURPOSE": "Introduce concepts of urban operations at the Squad and Platoon level. Develop Squad and Platoon SOPs for urban operations, react to UAS, BD6.\nKey Training Objectives: Battle Drill 6\nMovement in Urban Terrain\nUrban CCP/CASEVAC\nReact to UAS",
      "KEY TASKS": "include: ammo P/U, clearance of the range, day 0 weapons mx, SI inventory, day 0 recovery",
      "EXECUTION": "Phase 1: Planning. Begins with issuing of the OPORD, ends with SP to Land Nav W.",
      "TASKS": "Key Training Objectives: FOOM\nActions at a halt\nMount/Dismount\nReact to contact (direct/UAS)\nSquad Attack\nConcept:\nUnit that finishes the lane will act as the OPFOR\nHQ will act as the OPFOR for the react to contact lane with 1x .50cal emplacement\nN\n3rd PLT CP\n2nd PLT CP\n1st PLT CP\nCP\n30APR – Urban Ops Site (COA2)",
      "MISSION": "Comanche Troop, 1st Squadron, 2CR conducts Squad and Platoon Situational Training Exercises at the Urban Ops Site from 29APR24 to 01MAY24 IOT increase the lethality and cohesion of the Troop and maintain proficiency.\n29APR – Land Nav West"
    },
